    "en": {
      "name": "Argostars - Courageous Arion",
      "effect": "2 Level 4 monsters\nOnce per turn, you can also Xyz Summon \"Argostars - Courageous Arion\" by using 1 \"Argostars\" monster you control (transfer its materials to this card). If this card is Xyz Summoned: You can add 1 \"Argostars\" Spell from your Deck to your hand. During the Standby Phase: You can detach 2 materials from this card; place up to 3 \"Argostars\" Continuous Traps from your GY, face-up in your Spell & Trap Zone. You can only use each effect of \"Argostars - Courageous Arion\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
